original_title: Manhattan: Milligan Place - [Between West 10th and 11th Streets.]
text:
Milligan Place, Manhattan

Federal Art Project
"Changing New York"
Berenice Abbott, photographer

[Note: negative at Museum of the City of New York]
Code | A-2
Dec. 31, 1938

Milligan Place, located on the west side of Sixth Avenue, between West 10th and 11th Streets. Three of the four dwellings that stand here are shown. The photographer's back is to the avenue entrance and she is viewing westward.
